    "body": "numpy does this. This is technically a bug, but it _works_ because the floats are cast to ints.\n\n```\nIn [10]: arr = np.array([0,1,2])\n\nIn [11]: arr[0:2] = np.array([0.0,1.0], dtype='float64')\n\nIn [12]: arr\nOut[12]: array([0, 1, 2])\n```\n"
